{"tid":411810,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實真普選同港獨有咩分別?","createTime":"2017-09-24T06:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T08:43:16.000Z","uid":18521,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a11e53623eb8d8c4fd637871b5648b7cd4b1599","tid":411810,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"有左普選之後同獨立左其實分別唔大<br />\n<br />\n當一選左個偏本土既特首, 佢推行咩政策, 中國政府照理應該唔會可以理到<br />\n<br />\n如果08個陣中國比立法會+特首全面直選, 個陣全港仲係親中, 之後同中國既矛盾可能都唔會咁大<br />\n<br />\n但如果而家有既話, 發展落去最終都會有由官方發起既公投(無論係民意施壓定政府自己想都好)<br />\n<br />\n所以其實落實普選係咪可以話間接比香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c14c4323e51507ce04c834a1db6dee77041718","tid":411810,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"對中共黎講係無分別"},{"pid":"c6f8c6237a5ce7b6e9e4a83602006d44faa90617","tid":411810,"uid":86423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"正係香港班廢老就算有普選都一定唔會選到本土啦 何況候選人全部都有門檻 冇紅底你連入閘資格都冇"},{"pid":"99635e56d7b1a9561d58ff6fdc002de7037d2104","tid":411810,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"分別在真普選，最終決定權仲都係中共手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4421227bb5eee78cae4c0bc2192ed809bcfc198","tid":411810,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分別在真普選，最終決定權仲都係中共手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n選左特首之後, 中共可以肯定仲控制到特首一言一行?<br />\n<br />\n跟基本法, 唔比中國干涉香港內政, 真係仲係中共手上?"},{"pid":"6fa9d73e5a08635c3c19cd84852f2c3c8b28c462","tid":411810,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"一早已經係咁諗"},{"pid":"000215165d224120c828871433ad795311205f12","tid":411810,"uid":98477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分別在真普選，最終決定權仲都係中共手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚴格黎講，咁嘅&ldquo;普選&rdquo;唔係真，亦唔可以稱為普選"},{"pid":"5d3e5a7ab5add2fb2655764ba3d04c7d9529f82a","tid":411810,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5dbdb23dc1fe9df335132c245ee11640654d5e","tid":411810,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"民主即主權在民"},{"pid":"019f61fc13f476f5fe807371e01127e4e8a25526","tid":411810,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"華人既民族性都係貪錢<br />\n港獨？唔會有大多數市民支持，除非支爆<br />\n但係如果支爆，你想幾時獨立都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f604de2cfe0dd212058a221d1e4c67bb94897657","tid":411810,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>華人既民族性都係貪錢<br />\n港獨？唔會有大多數市民支持，除非支爆<br />\n但係如果支爆，你想幾時獨立都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到其他民族唔貪錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40675d92b336890b574752c9c2be3a473a18c4f","tid":411810,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>華人既民族性都係貪錢<br />\n港獨？唔會有大多數市民支持，除非支爆<br />\n但係如果支爆，你想幾時獨立都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到其他民族唔貪錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n關其他人撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔係講緊外國<br />\n唔通蘇格蘭人貪錢唔脫英又會影響到香港人？"}]}